headline: The Smartest High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy With $1,000 Right Now
summary: AT&T's refocus on its core telecom business has made the business more stable than in previous years.  There's seemingly never a dull moment in the stock market, and this year has been no different.  Given the uncertainty surrounding the stock market and economy right now, dividend stocks look more appealing than usual.
